<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="185" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1127,1069,1252]" pageId="2" pageNumber="185">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,298,1133,1156]" pageId="2" pageNumber="185">Distribution.</emphasis>
A species widely distributed in the entire Palaearctic Region, but absent in the Arabian Peninsula (
<bibRefCitation author="ASCHER J. S. &amp; PICKERING J." box="[398,681,1165,1188]" pageId="2" pageNumber="185" refId="ref14368" refString="ASCHER J. S. &amp; PICKERING J. 2017: Discover Life bee species guide and world checklist (Hymenoptera: Apoidea: Anthophila). Available from: http: // www. discoverlife. org / mp / 20 q? guide = Apoidea _ species (April 26, 2017)." type="url" year="2017">ASCHER &amp; PICKERING 2017</bibRefCitation>
). In 
<collectingCountry box="[726,807,1165,1188]" name="Yemen" pageId="2" pageNumber="185">Socotra</collectingCountry>
reported from Moukaradia (= Gebel Raggit), Homhil, Dinehan Valley, Adho Dimellus (
<bibRefCitation author="KIRBY W. F." box="[765,894,1197,1220]" pageId="2" pageNumber="185" pagination="1898 - 9" refId="ref15844" refString="KIRBY W. F. 1903: Insecta: Hymenoptera. Pp. 235 - 258. In: FORBES H. O. (ed.): The natural history of Sokotra and Abd-el-Kuri: Being the report upon the results of the conjoint expedition to these islands in 1898 - 9. Special Bulletin of the Liverpool Museums, xlvii + 598 pp." type="book chapter" year="1903">KIRBY 1903</bibRefCitation>
); Ras Shoab, Haghier Mts., and from Samha island (
<bibRefCitation author="KOHL F. F." box="[474,595,1229,1252]" pageId="2" pageNumber="185" refId="ref15911" refString="KOHL F. F. 1906: Zoologische Ergebnisse der Expedition der Kaiserlichen Akademie der Wissenschaften nach Sudarabien und Sokotra im Jahre 1898 - 1899. Hymenopteren. Kaiserlichen Akademie der Wissenschaften, Wien, 133 pp + XI pls. [Preprint of KOHL (1907)]." type="book" year="1906">KOHL 1906</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="KOHL F. F." box="[606,663,1229,1252]" pageId="2" pageNumber="185" pagination="169 - 301" refId="ref15961" refString="KOHL F. F. 1907: Zoologische Ergebnisse der Expedition der Kaiserlichen Akademie der Wissenschaften nach Sudarabien und Sokotra im Jahre 1898 - 1899. Hymenopteren. Denkschriften der Kaiserlichen Akademie der Wissenschaften, Mathematisch-Naturwissenschaftliche Klasse 71: 169 - 301 + pls I - XI." type="journal article" year="1907">1907</bibRefCitation>
).
